{"tid":905868,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"三十年一直都未被超越既神作-阿基拉","createTime":"2018-11-17T13:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T08:00:16.000Z","uid":134683,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a2ef4ca44aca5e675d9e797cac8eb70ec1b09d","tid":905868,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXy4rvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXy4rvb.jpg&h=d57ef55c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1開拍前已經好多人質疑有冇可能拍得成，因為原作畫功太仔細<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xJvyjRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxJvyjRE.jpg&h=be5e9784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1m9CDk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1m9CDk.jpg&h=29a1a396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左要做到原作神髓<br />\n總共用左16萬張膠片<br />\n比天空之城仲多<br />\n製作費亦係破紀錄11億日圓<br />\n要7間大公司(Bandai,東寶....)合資<br />\n<br />\n2同一般事後配音唔同<br />\n大友克洋安排先錄音後作畫<br />\n優點係戲劇感更强<br />\n但就要畫師根據配音員錄音去作畫<br />\n大幅增加制作難度<br />\n<br />\n3配樂亦係電影史上經典<br />\n大膽起用業餘既藝能山城組<br />\n將日本傳統樂器、印尼基朗美敲擊樂、西洋管風琴等混合，再以當時有限技術做電子合成，而大友克洋亦對藝能山城組絕對信任，先作曲而後制作動畫"},{"pid":"bc5ffb0ec94dd4d040c6f675a81f9c3788ccf792","tid":905868,"uid":34293,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"依套真係屈機  到家陣睇都唔會覺得入面既野過時<br />\n家陣狗屎垃圾都好意思話係神作"},{"pid":"76bf91a754b225111c1252a97cbc9452618d1910","tid":905868,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc5ffb0ec94dd4d040c6f675a81f9c3788ccf792","tid":905868,"uid":34293,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"依套真係屈機  到家陣睇都唔會覺得入面既野過時<br />\n家陣狗屎垃圾都好意思話係神作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"依家電影制作太制度化<br />\n已經唔可能由得個導演有絕對話事權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca60b6161e4aab96d4349f6400ec9d833af43b5c","tid":905868,"uid":3969